object.customQuery:
SELECT
A.Policy_Key,
A.Policy_Key_Code,
A.Major_Peril_ID,
A.Risk_State_ID,
A.Account_Entered_Dt,
A.MTD_Earned_Premium,
A.Unearned_Premium,
A.Commission_Amount,
A.Taxes_Svc_Charges,
A.Written_Premium,
A.PT_ID,
A.StateLine,
A.annual_statement_line,
B.Policy_Transaction_ID,
TGT.row_id,
TGT.md5_hash_value
FROM
	dbo.PMS_Fact_Premiums_Earned A
	LEFT JOIN dbo.PMS_Policy_Transactions B
	ON abs(A.PT_ID) = B.Policy_Transaction_ID
	left join dbo.msgr_facts_pms_new_vw1 TGT on
		A.Policy_Key = TGT.Policy_Key AND
		A.Policy_Key_Code = TGT.Policy_Key_Code AND
		A.Major_Peril_ID = TGT.Major_Peril_ID AND
		A.Risk_State_ID = TGT.Risk_State_ID AND
		A.Account_Entered_Dt = TGT.Account_Entered_Dt AND
		NVL(A.StateLine,'NA') = NVL(TGT.StateLine,'NA') AND
		NVL(A.annual_statement_line,'NA') = NVL(TGT.annual_statement_line,'NA')
WHERE
--YEAR(Account_Entered_Dt) = 2023
--and	A.StateLine is not null
--Account_Entered_Dt >=dateadd(month, -1, cast(getdate() as date)) AND
date_part(year,A.account_entered_dt) in ('2024') AND 
--2005 and 2006 '2007','2008','2009' 2010','2011','2012','2013' '2014','2015','2016','2017' 2018, 2019, 2020, 2021  '2022','2023','2024 done. Initial load for testing was completed several years at a time
(A.row_ins_dt >= (SELECT etlbatchstartst FROM dbo.loadbatchetldt WHERE loadetltype = 'wf_msgr_views')
OR B.row_ins_dt >= (SELECT etlbatchstartst FROM dbo.loadbatchetldt WHERE loadetltype = 'wf_msgr_views'))
ORDER BY
A.Policy_Key,
A.Policy_Key_Code,
A.Major_Peril_ID,
A.Risk_State_ID,
A.Account_Entered_Dt,
A.StateLine,
A.annual_statement_line,
TGT.row_id,
TGT.md5_hash_value

attributes.name: Download S3 Files In Multiple Parts

fields.name: Flag
fields.expression: IIF(ISNULL(row_id),'I',IIF(NOT ISNULL(row_id) AND (in_MD5_Hash<>md5_hash_value),'U',IIF(NOT ISNULL(row_id) AND ISNULL(md5_hash_value),'U','R')))
